{"code":"import pandas as pd

# Load the CSV file into a DataFrame
file_path = '8d46b8d6-b38a-47ff-ac74-cda14cf2d19b.csv'
df = pd.read_csv(file_path)

# Filter out penguins that live on Dream Island or have beaks longer than 42mm
filtered_df = df[(df['island'] != 'Dream') & (df['bill_length_mm'] <= 42)]

# Count the number of penguins that meet the criteria
filtered_penguin_count = len(filtered_df)

# Print the count of filtered penguins
filtered_penguin_count","packages":["pandas"]}

{"code":"import pandas as pd

# Load the CSV file into a DataFrame
file_path = '8d46b8d6-b38a-47ff-ac74-cda14cf2d19b.csv'
df = pd.read_csv(file_path)

# Filter out penguins that live on Dream Island or have beaks longer than 42mm
filtered_df = df[(df['island'] != 'Dream') & (df['bill_length_mm'] <= 42)]

# Count the number of penguins that meet the criteria
filtered_penguin_count = len(filtered_df)

# Print the count of filtered penguins
filtered_penguin_count","packages":["pandas"]}
